name: ObjectLOGO
description: ObjectLOGO is a variant of the programming language Logo with object-oriented programming extensions. Lexical scope. Version 2.7 is sold by Digitool, Inc. It is no longer being developed or supported, and does not run on versions of the Mac operating system after version 7.5.
